{"tid":1432363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實要對準林鄭成日講嘅「少數」極端分子","createTime":"2019-08-08T08:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T13:33:54.000Z","uid":252178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e2cb6a4fd9c20da6cb0e51b81b69c22ae110df58","tid":1432363,"uid":252178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:23:17.000Z","msg":"民主社會都會有「少數服從多數」嘅概念<br />\n佢想普遍市民覺得出黎示威嘅人屬於少數<br />\n之前聽一個浸大前學生會會長講<br />\n對話係無用 因為大家各自講自己立場係無意思<br />\n要代表真正民意 要代表誰才是大多數<br />\n首先要有一個民主制度 果個就係雙普選<br />\n所以下次一有人講起對話 我覺得可以試下講以上呢個論點<br />\n<br />\n另外其實仍然有好多人唔記得五大訴求係乜<br />\n如期成日講改乜野口號 不如<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">直接每個訴求叫出黎</span></span></strong><br />\n尤其係普選 呢個要嗌多啲<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求為<br />\n1. 徹底撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 撤回 612 暴動定性<br />\n3. 必不追究反送中抗爭者<br />\n4. 成立獨立委員會，徹查警方濫權濫暴及元朗暴力事件<br />\n5. 全面落實雙真普選"},{"pid":"93c67f06436e17355832116c3891fa32b77c166e","tid":1432363,"uid":252178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:26:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a72789e74efbbffcc7a6976fc6107eda0f056c42","tid":1432363,"uid":252178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:29:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eed4e4f35ae01afb96366d7bb7d14256606f54b2","tid":1432363,"uid":252178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:31:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c059d319ee6d733dad76a25981bd1541d245c0c","tid":1432363,"uid":252178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:14:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"367cb6eee6fd8cb3fc989faf91c601f22df58227","tid":1432363,"uid":236538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:16:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fKKAV07.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfKKAV07.png&h=457cef39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"642cb96a2c0156846d8a71b6f52b2e095d2981c1","tid":1432363,"uid":252178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:33:54.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}